text: William Macnish (29 October 1842 - 29 November 1873) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1862/63. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1842 births Category:1873 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
